# GMAIL

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User ig.paraskun@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass google.com/mail/pass"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail-general
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Both
Expunge Both

Channel gmail-sent
Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Near :gmail-local:Sent
Create Near
Expunge Both

Channel gmail-trash
Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Near :gmail-local:Trash
Create Near
Expunge Both

Group gmail
Channel gmail-general
Channel gmail-sent
Channel gmail-trash

# NSTU

IMAPAccount nstu
